<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.10.10">
<l>villār malivēṅ kaṭamā malaimēya</l>
<l>mallārt tiraṭōḷ maṇivaṇ ṇaṉammāṉai</l>
<l>kallārt tiraṭōḷ kaliyaṉ coṉṉamālai</l>
<l>vallā ravarvā ṉavarā kuvartāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master the garland composed by Kaliyaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">with boulder-like bulging arms</l>
<l>About the jewel-hued lord with strength-filled bulging arms</l>
<l>Who dwells on the great mountain Vēṅkaṭam, where archers abound,</l>
<l>They will themselves become celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
